import React from 'react'
import { FotterContainer,FotterWrap,FotterLinksContainer,FotterLinksWrapper,FotterLink } from './FotterElements'

        <FotterContainer>
            <FotterWrap>
                <FotterLinksContainer>
                    <FotterLinksWrapper>
                        <FotterLinkItems>

                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Testomonialys</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Carrers</FotterLink>

                        </FotterLinkItems>
                        <FotterLinkItems>

                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>How it works</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Testomonialys</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Carrers</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Investors</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Terms of Service</FotterLink>
                        </FotterLinkItems>
                    </FotterLinksWrapper>
                    <FotterLinksWrapper>
                        <FotterLinkItems>

                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>About us</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>How it works</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Testomonialys</FotterLink>

                        </FotterLinkItems>
                        <FotterLinkItems>
                            <FotterLinkTitle>About us</FotterLinkTitle>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>About us</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>How it works</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Testomonialys</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Carrers</FotterLink>
                                <FotterLink to='/signin'>Investors</FotterLink>

                        </FotterLinkItems>
                    </FotterLinksWrapper>
                </FotterLinksContainer>
            </FotterWrap>
        </FotterContainer>

    )
}

export default Fotter
